  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThe readmes of each individual package in the monorepo do not adequately link back to ChainSafe and Lodestar.\r\nEach readme doesn't convey the context that the package is part of something bigger, nor does it mention ChainSafe.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n- Include a header in each package in the monorepo, consistently placed, something like:\r\n\r\n> This package is part of [ChainSafe's Lodestar](https://lodestar.chainsafe.io) project\r\n\r\n- Include a link/reference to ChainSafe & chainsafe.io in the footer, perhaps with the license:\r\n\r\nLGPL-3.0 [ChainSafe Systems](https://chainsafe.io)\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nAdd a ChainSafe / Lodestar badge?\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nSee how lodestar-types README is rendered / viewed by a newcomer coming across lodestar via npm or github\r\n- https://www.npmjs.com/package/@chainsafe/lodestar-types\r\n- https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/tree/master/packages/lodestar-types",
